  "body": "# Problem\n\nAs part of https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6375\nwe started hitting some FlatList limitations.\nThe one that we most struggled with is inserting messages on both ends so we can implement pagination on both sides.\nIn this spike we should try out different react native list implementations to see if there's a suitable replacement out-of-the-box.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- LIst should be performant\n- We should be able to paginate both sides\n- We should be able to maintain scroll position\n\nPlease timebox it to a suitable time.",
